#   **100-LIBRARY-PER-LANGUAGE LANDMARK (Rust side)**
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This completion **OPENS AXIS 45** in the cross-
# language CLI library taxonomy AND marks the
# **100-LIBRARY-PER-LANGUAGE LANDMARK on the Rust
# side** — a major milestone parallel to the
# previously crossed Rust 90-library landmark at
# R729 (chirpstack), the Go 100-library landmark at
# R??, and the TS-Node landmarks at R??.  The next
